quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óanke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e …ìaawo heedo, maa O immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e du≈ãayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O Toowu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gom…óinal; si ko woni, Men wa…óunde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin ruttotoo"
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
  43,2,Mi woondirii Defere …ìanngunde nden
  43,3,"Men wa…óii nde janngeteende [e …óemngal] aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  43,4,"Pellet, hinde woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma Defte, toowunde, √±e√±aande"
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinangol on jantoore nden, …óuurngal on, fii on wonii yim…ìe fantim…ìe"
  43,6,∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ìe …ìe Men nuli e adinoo…ìe …ìen
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa …ìe jalkitay mo"
  43,8,Men halki ko …ìuri …ìe sa…ótude doole ! Toode mise adinoo…ìe …ìen yawtiino
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin?\" ∆Åe wi'ay: \"Ko Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On tagi …ói"
  43,10,"On wa…óiran…óo on leydi ndin weertaandi, O wa…óani on …óate e mayri, fii no …óoworon"
  43,11,"On jippinr…óo to…ìo ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Men wuurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko non yaltinirte…óon"
  43,12,"On tagu…óo nooneeji …óin fow, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óin, ko wa…ó…óoron"
  43,13,"fii yo on fotondir e hoore majji, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma fotondir…óon e majji, wi'on ontuma: \"Senayee woodanii eltan…óo men …óum On, men wonaano taaqanaa…ìe …óum"
  43,14,"menen non, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko men ruttotoo"
  43,15,"∆Åe wa…óani Mo ge…ìal e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen ! Pellet, on ne…ó…óanke ko yeddu…óo …ìanngu…óo"
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wewliniraama ko o wa…óirani kon Hinaranke On misal, yeeso makko ngon ni…ì…ìita metteendi hombo suu…ói"
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, wanaa o …ìannginoowo haala"
  43,19,"∆Åe wa…ói Malaa'ikaa…ìe taw…ìe …ìen ko jeyaa…ìe Jom Hinaranke On, rew…ìe ! Kere …ìe seedino tageede …ìen? Awa fii seedagol ma…ì…ìe ngol winndete, …ìe lamnditoyee"
  43,20,"∆Åe wi'iti: \"Si Jom Hinaranke On haajuno, men rewataano …ìe\". ∆Åe alanaa …óum hay e ganndal; …ìe wonaali, si wanaa hi…ìe fena"
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani …ìe ado ndee …óoo, hara ko nden woni ko …ìe jogitii"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, …ìe wi'iu: \"Menen men tawu baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e diina, haray ko e batteeji ma…ì…ìe men feewirta"
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Men nulaali jertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wanaa hooree…ìe ma…ì…ìe neemii…ìe wi'ay: \"Menen men tawu baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ì…ìe …óin men √±entinta"